<div class="about-container" id="about-us">
    <div class="row">
        <h1 style="margin-top:10%">About</h1>


    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="six columns">
            <h3><span class="typcn typcn-device-desktop icon"></span>Our Process</h3>
            <p>
                Follow the process exactly, not deviating from it or using your own knowledge. Make edits to anything that needs to be clarified.Follow the process and trust the leader.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="six columns">
            <h3><span class="typcn typcn-pen icon"></span>Our Approach</h3>
            <p>
                Each member of the team is responsible for owning their work, collaborating effectively with  team members, and striving for excellence.
            </p>
