            <div class="six columns">
                <h3><span class="typcn typcn-lightbulb icon"></span>Our Mission</h3>
                <p>  The phrase “this journey is 1% finished” is posted on our walls, reminding us that we’ve only begun to fulfill our mission to make the world  work closer together.</p>
            </div>
    </div>
</div>


